# If the verbose mode is activated, switchcord will
# log more during building. This information may
# include statistics, dependencies and versions.
option(switchcord_VERBOSE "Enable this for verbose logging." OFF)

# If activated, the language standard will be set to C++17,
# otherwise the C++11 standard will be used.
option(switchcord_USE_CPP_17 "Enable this for the C++17 language standard." ON)